<pb n="0169b" xml:id="T21.1232.0169b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0169b01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0169b02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1232</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0169b03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0169001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本</note>播<note n="0169002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">般＝那【甲】</note><note n="0169002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">般【大】，那【甲】</note><app n="0169002"><lem wit="【大】">般</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg></app>曩結使波<note place="inline">唐云步擲</note>金剛念誦儀</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0169b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0169b05" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0169b0501"><l>歸命金剛手</l><l>諸佛所依者</l>
<lb n="0169b06" ed="T"/><l>具普賢眾行</l><l>住是本有身</l>
<lb n="0169b07" ed="T"/><l>無始無終寂</l><l>妙用施諸願</l>
<lb n="0169b08" ed="T"/><l><note n="0169003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝魔【甲】</note><note n="0169003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩【大】，魔【甲】</note><app n="0169003"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">魔</rdg></app>王順三毒</l><l>改劫<note n="0169004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">故＝放【甲】</note><note n="0169004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故【大】，放【甲】</note><app n="0169004"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">放</rdg></app>調柔</l>
<lb n="0169b09" ed="T"/><l>拯救諸有情</l><l>從凡入佛地</l>
<lb n="0169b10" ed="T"/><l>現世皆成就</l><l>今演念誦義</l></lg>
<lb n="0169b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b1101">次若<note n="0169005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169005"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷。樂修步
<lb n="0169b12" ed="T"/>擲明王心真言者。當如法治地建立道場。修
<lb n="0169b13" ed="T"/>先行門面東而<note n="0169006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔坐〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169006"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。所須供養飲食香華。隨
<lb n="0169b14" ed="T"/>力當陳務令清潔。入道場已遍禮諸佛。一心
<lb n="0169b15" ed="T"/>歸依願登正覺。然後結跏趺坐或復半跏。以
<lb n="0169b16" ed="T"/>香泥塗手備諸印契。次明三部及護身。<note n="0169007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">知＝如【甲】</note><note n="0169007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知【大】，如【甲】</note><app n="0169007"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">如</rdg></app>諸
<lb n="0169b17" ed="T"/>教儀此略不抄。</p>
<lb n="0169b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b1801">次乃端身正坐息諸緣慮。當觀己身皆由先
<lb n="0169b19" ed="T"/>世之因。成此四大五蘊。於一一求實不得無
<lb n="0169b20" ed="T"/>常敗壞。速起速滅即色即空。如是了了決定
<lb n="0169b21" ed="T"/>信解已。其能觀之不可泯滅。成真實智。廓周
<lb n="0169b22" ed="T"/>法界。量等虛空。以大悲故從真起用。乃想己
<lb n="0169b23" ed="T"/>身形如本尊威儀亦等不一不異。</p>
<lb n="0169b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b2401">復結前三昧金剛杵契。以印於心誦<note n="0169008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169008"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>真言
<lb n="0169b25" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0169b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b2601" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>纈哩<note place="inline">二<note n="0169009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（二）【甲】</note><note n="0169009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合二【甲】</note><app n="0169009"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合二</rdg></app></note>儒𡄦<note place="inline">二合三</note></p>
<lb n="0169b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b2701">由此契及真言加持。行者心如本尊。</p>
<lb n="0169b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b2801">及舉契印頭誦真言。</p>
<lb n="0169b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169b2901" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>部𡄦<note place="inline">二合二</note></p>
<pb n="0169c" xml:id="T21.1232.0169c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0169c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c0101">由此契及真言加持故。猶同本尊。</p>
<lb n="0169c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c0201">亦以契印額右肩左肩及心喉。皆誦被甲<note n="0169010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔冑〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冑【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169010"><lem wit="【大】">冑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0169c03" ed="T"/>真<note n="0169011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＋（曰）【甲】</note><note n="0169011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，言曰【甲】</note><app n="0169011"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">言曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0169c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c0401" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>儒𡄦<note place="inline">二合二</note></p>
<lb n="0169c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c0501">由此契及真言加持故。即成被金剛甲冑無
<lb n="0169c06" ed="T"/>能嬈害。由如前觀行及誦真言加持故。行者
<lb n="0169c07" ed="T"/>之身與本尊無異。諸佛受記龍天歸仰。決定
<lb n="0169c08" ed="T"/>成無上正等菩提。</p>
<lb n="0169c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c0901">金剛橛契</p>
<lb n="0169c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c1001">契相以右無名指入左無名指小指間。中指
<lb n="0169c11" ed="T"/>入左中指頭指間。左亦如之。餘指並頭相拄。
<lb n="0169c12" ed="T"/>想成火焰金剛杵形。以大指著地。卓而掣
<lb n="0169c13" ed="T"/><note n="0169012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＋（若）ヵ【原】</note><note n="0169012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，之若【考偽-原】</note><app n="0169012"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">之若</rdg></app>。掣一誦至三而止。隨意大小標心。即成
<lb n="0169c14" ed="T"/>金剛堅固地界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0169c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c1501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>枳里枳里嚩日羅<note place="inline">二合二</note>嚩日里部羅<note place="inline">三</note>滿
<lb n="0169c16" ed="T"/>馱滿馱<note n="0169013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔四〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169013"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>𤙖泮吒</p>
<lb n="0169c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c1701">由此結契及真言加持故。下至金剛際悉如
<lb n="0169c18" ed="T"/>金剛座。天魔及諸障者不為惱害。</p>
<lb n="0169c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c1901">次方隅金剛牆界。</p>
<lb n="0169c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c2001">契相准前地界。開二大指竪之。側如牆形。右
<lb n="0169c21" ed="T"/>遶身三轉。標心大小即成金剛堅固之城。諸
<lb n="0169c22" ed="T"/><note n="0169014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169014"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩尚不違越。何況諸餘難調伏者。悉不
<lb n="0169c23" ed="T"/>能近。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0169c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c2401" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>沙羅沙羅<note n="0169015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169015"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日囉鉢囉迦<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0169016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">邏＝羅【甲】</note><note n="0169016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">邏【大】，羅【甲】</note><app n="0169016"><lem wit="【大】">邏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">三</note>吽泮
<lb n="0169c25" ed="T"/>吒</p>
<lb n="0169c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0169c2601">行者次當想於壇中有八葉蓮華。上有師子
<lb n="0169c27" ed="T"/>之座。座上有七寶樓<note n="0169017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔閣〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閣【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169017"><lem wit="【大】">閣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。垂諸瓔珞繒綵幡
<lb n="0169c28" ed="T"/>蓋。寶柱行列垂妙天衣。周布香雲。普雨雜花
<lb n="0169c29" ed="T"/>奏諸音樂。<note n="0169018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寶〕－【甲】</note><note n="0169018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0169018"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>瓶<note n="0169019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（開）＋閼【甲】</note><note n="0169019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閼【大】，開閼【甲】</note><app n="0169019"><lem wit="【大】">閼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">開閼</rdg></app>伽天妙飲食摩尼為燈。
<pb n="0170a" xml:id="T21.1232.0170a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170a01" ed="T"/>作是觀已。</p>
<lb n="0170a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a0201">結大虛空藏契。契相合掌當心。蹙二頭指如
<lb n="0170a03" ed="T"/>寶形。并舒二大指押頭指根。二中指右押左
<lb n="0170a04" ed="T"/>外相交。互著手皆契成。誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a0501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>伽伽那三婆嚩嚩<note n="0170a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">日【CB】，曰【大】</note><app n="0170a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉斛</p><p xml:id="pT21p0170a0513" rend="inline">由結此契及
<lb n="0170a06" ed="T"/>誦真言加持故。所想供養等物。真實無異聖
<lb n="0170a07" ed="T"/>眾受用。</p>
<lb n="0170a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a0801">寶車輅契</p>
<lb n="0170a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a0901">契相二手內相叉仰掌。頭指橫相拄。以二大
<lb n="0170a10" ed="T"/>指各捻頭指根下。想成七寶車輅。金剛賀御
<lb n="0170a11" ed="T"/>乘空而去。至於本尊之宮。誦真言三遍。真言
<lb n="0170a12" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0170a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a1301" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>都嚕都嚕<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0170001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吽＋（三）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0170001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吽【大】，吽(三)【甲】</note><app n="0170001"><lem wit="【大】">吽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吽<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0170a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a1401">由結此印及真言加持故。七<note n="0170002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶車輅＝輅車【甲】</note><note n="0170002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶車輅【大】，輅車【甲】</note><app n="0170002"><lem wit="【大】">寶車輅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">輅車</rdg></app>至尊宮
<lb n="0170a15" ed="T"/>殿。想大聖本尊及諸眷屬昇輅車。</p>
<lb n="0170a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a1601">請車輅契</p>
<lb n="0170a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a1701">契相準前契。<note n="0170003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">互＝印【甲】</note><note n="0170003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">互【大】，印【甲】</note><app n="0170003"><lem wit="【大】">互</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印</rdg></app>以大指向身撥中指。誦真言
<lb n="0170a18" ed="T"/>三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a1901" cb:type="dharani">那莫悉底哩野地尾迦南薩<note n="0170004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】</note><note n="0170004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，縛【甲】</note><app n="0170004"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>怛他蘖多南
<lb n="0170a20" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二</note>唵<note n="0170005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170005"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日<note n="0170006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唧＝即【甲】</note><note n="0170006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唧【大】，即【甲】</note><app n="0170006"><lem wit="【大】">唧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>擬那野<note place="inline">引</note>迦囉沙野曀呬裔
<lb n="0170a21" ed="T"/>呬<note place="inline">若奉送除來句加去句</note>薄伽晚<note place="inline"><note n="0170007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六＝二合【甲】</note><note n="0170007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六【大】，二合【甲】</note><app n="0170007"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合</rdg></app></note>馺嚩訶<note n="0170008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔七〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170008"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">七</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0170a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a2201">由結此契誦真言加持故。聖眾從本宮來。赴
<lb n="0170a23" ed="T"/>於道場依空而住。</p>
<lb n="0170a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a2401">本尊三昧耶降道場契。契相二手內相叉作
<lb n="0170a25" ed="T"/>拳。右大指入。掌左大指向身招之。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a2601" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>嚩日囉地哩迦<note n="0170009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170009"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曀呬裔呬<note place="inline">三若奉送除𪾼呬裔呬加伽車</note>
<lb n="0170a27" ed="T"/>薄伽梵<note place="inline">四</note>嚩日囉地<note n="0170010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哩＝里【甲】</note><note n="0170010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哩【大】，里【甲】</note><app n="0170010"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">里</rdg></app>迦<note place="inline">五</note></p>
<lb n="0170a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170a2801">由此真言契加持故。本尊不違本誓。集於道
<lb n="0170a29" ed="T"/>場。</p>
<pb n="0170b" xml:id="T21.1232.0170b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b0101">步擲契</p>
<lb n="0170b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b0201">契相先正立。舉右足向左斷空。逐日右轉使
<lb n="0170b03" ed="T"/>頓地。又移左足就右如初立。乃舉左足向右
<lb n="0170b04" ed="T"/>斷空。<note n="0170011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔因〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">因【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170011"><lem wit="【大】">因</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>向左頓地屈膝。乃舉左手頭指已下
<lb n="0170b05" ed="T"/>成拳。以大指押頭指側。想執三股杵極力展
<lb n="0170b06" ed="T"/>臂向左擬勢。右手大指入掌。以中名指握之。
<lb n="0170b07" ed="T"/>頭指及小指皆舒之。極力垂臂手背向外。<note n="0170012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">死出現＝利牙各現【甲】</note><note n="0170012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">死出現【大】，利牙各現【甲】</note><app n="0170012"><lem wit="【大】">死
<lb n="0170b08" ed="T"/>出現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">利牙各現</rdg></app>嗔目左顧想。餘臂悉如本尊執持。亦菩
<lb n="0170b09" ed="T"/>薩等。每想器拭之手。皆誦器拭真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b1001" cb:type="dharani">唵虐</p>
<lb n="0170b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b1101">又想舉身三威焰由如劫燒。徹至十方一切
<lb n="0170b12" ed="T"/>世界。廣作佛事照觸言悟。一切如來初成道
<lb n="0170b13" ed="T"/>者願速轉法輪。度眾生者破其<note n="0170013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">小器＝少執【甲】</note><note n="0170013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">小器【大】，少執【甲】</note><app n="0170013"><lem wit="【大】">小器</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">少執</rdg></app>。臨涅
<lb n="0170b14" ed="T"/>槃者勸請久住。次當勸發菩薩之眾願。皆速
<lb n="0170b15" ed="T"/>證無上菩提。於其中間慎無退屈。復當啟發
<lb n="0170b16" ed="T"/>二乘之人。除其小兒令具大乘甚深空慧。凡
<lb n="0170b17" ed="T"/>夫之界威光所及。樊藏識中雜染種子。永離
<lb n="0170b18" ed="T"/>三途具普賢行。傍生餓鬼盡此一形不復更
<lb n="0170b19" ed="T"/>受。亦想樊諸地獄。壞滅無餘罪人。解脫發菩
<lb n="0170b20" ed="T"/>提心諸惡魔等。遇者摧伏辟除退散。如是量
<lb n="0170b21" ed="T"/>久利益既畢。想收威焰集於身中。然後出定。
<lb n="0170b22" ed="T"/>次復如<note n="0170014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170014"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>初依法。而坐。</p>
<lb n="0170b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b2301">上方金剛網契</p>
<lb n="0170b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b2401">契相準前牆契二大指捻頭指下節。誦真言
<lb n="0170b25" ed="T"/>三<note n="0170015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迊＝遍【甲】</note><note n="0170015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迊【大】，遍【甲】</note><app n="0170015"><lem wit="【大】">迊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">遍</rdg></app>。頭上右轉三<note n="0170016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170016"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>迊。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b2601" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>尾塞普羅<note place="inline">二</note>娜𡀩乞叉嚩日囉半惹囉<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0170b27" ed="T"/>𤙖泮吒</p>
<lb n="0170b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b2801">由此網契真言加持故。當成金剛堅固之網。</p>
<lb n="0170b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170b2901">火院密縫旋契。契相左手掩右手背竪二大
<pb n="0170c" xml:id="T21.1232.0170c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170c01" ed="T"/>指。誦真言三遍。右繞身三匝。想金剛牆外。火
<lb n="0170c02" ed="T"/>焰圍繞。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c0301" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>阿娑莽擬儞<note place="inline">二</note>𤙖泮吒</p>
<lb n="0170c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c0401">次捧閼伽器近額想浴聖眾之足。</p>
<lb n="0170c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c0501">普供養契</p>
<lb n="0170c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c0601">契相二手合掌右押左交。指初分即成。誦真
<lb n="0170c07" ed="T"/>言三遍。諦想無量無邊塗香雲海末香雲海
<lb n="0170c08" ed="T"/>燒香雲海花鬘雲海燈明雲海飲食雲海衣服
<lb n="0170c09" ed="T"/>雲海。及一切供養等物皆成清淨廣多供養
<lb n="0170c10" ed="T"/>普供養真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0170c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c1101" cb:type="dharani">那莫薩嚩怛他蘖帝彌逾<note place="inline">二合一</note>尾濕嚩暮契藐
<lb n="0170c12" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二</note>薩嚩他欠<note place="inline">三</note>鄔娜伽帝<note place="inline">四</note>娑頗羅系<g ref="#CB04186"/><note place="inline">五</note>誐誐
<lb n="0170c13" ed="T"/>曩劍<note place="inline">六</note>馺嚩訶</p>
<lb n="0170c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c1401">本尊心真言<note n="0170017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170017"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0170c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c1501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>纈𡄦<note place="inline">二合二</note>尾𡄦<note place="inline">二合三</note>部𡄦<note place="inline">二合四</note>素𡄦<note place="inline">二合五</note>儒𡄦
<lb n="0170c16" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合六</note>虐</p>
<lb n="0170c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c1701">次復思惟己身與本尊無異。持金剛子珠。誦
<lb n="0170c18" ed="T"/>次前心真言。正念誦時觀本尊形像。或觀真
<lb n="0170c19" ed="T"/>言所<note n="0170018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">有＋（之）【甲】</note><note n="0170018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，有之【甲】</note><app n="0170018"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">有之</rdg></app>文字。或觀本尊心上有真言字。或寂
<lb n="0170c20" ed="T"/>靜心相應念誦。不急不緩亦不<note n="0170019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">太＝大【甲】</note><note n="0170019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">太【大】，大【甲】</note><app n="0170019"><lem wit="【大】">太</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>小。課限畢
<lb n="0170c21" ed="T"/>己心欲<note n="0170020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔除〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170020"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>息際。仍<note n="0170021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔須〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">須【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170021"><lem wit="【大】">須</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>良久住本尊觀。復獻
<lb n="0170c22" ed="T"/>閼伽亦結普<note n="0170022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔供〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170022"><lem wit="【大】">供</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>養運心供養誦本真言。次結
<lb n="0170c23" ed="T"/>火院密縫契。頭上左轉一匝即成。解界次結
<lb n="0170c24" ed="T"/>降道場契向外撥之。想聖眾歸宮。次結護身
<lb n="0170c25" ed="T"/>契。準前印五處。各誦<note n="0170023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔本〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170023"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>真言。</p>
<lb n="0170c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0170c2601">次誦大輪金剛真言二十一遍真言<note place="inline">此略不寫抄如餘本所謂
<lb n="0170c27" ed="T"/>一種取用</note>由誦此真<note n="0170024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【甲】</note><note n="0170024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0170024"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>故。所有違犯軌則之愆。悉
<lb n="0170c28" ed="T"/>滅無餘功不虛棄。其息災增益降伏三事法。
<lb n="0170c29" ed="T"/>廣如蘇悉地經中所陳。任作成就當知福祐
<pb n="0171a" xml:id="T21.1232.0171a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0171a01" ed="T"/>畫像法。用應肘量𦁛如儀清淨。圖畫本尊遍
<lb n="0171a02" ed="T"/>身青色。右顧舒右足屈左膝。右上手垂下。屈
<lb n="0171a03" ed="T"/>大指入掌。中名指握之。舒餘二指手背向外。
<lb n="0171a04" ed="T"/>次手持桃垂下。次<note n="0171001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">下＝手【甲】</note><note n="0171001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下【大】，手【甲】</note><app n="0171001"><lem wit="【大】">下</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">手</rdg></app>舒掌向下。掌中<note n="0171002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】</note><note n="0171002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0171002"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>火
<lb n="0171a05" ed="T"/>焰。次手鐵斧。次玉環次竪擬指。指上有輪。次
<lb n="0171a06" ed="T"/>拳大指押頭指側。次羂索。次舒五指。甲長而
<lb n="0171a07" ed="T"/>利仰掌。末手持弓。右近上手三股杵。舒臂向
<lb n="0171a08" ed="T"/>上。次劍。次握圓石。次短柄槌槌如重輪。次兩
<lb n="0171a09" ed="T"/>隻箭。次杖。次獨股杵。次舒掌。掌仰頭指大指
<lb n="0171a10" ed="T"/>相捻勢。次寶棒棒上麁近<note n="0171003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">把＝犯【甲】</note><note n="0171003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">把【大】，犯【甲】</note><app n="0171003"><lem wit="【大】">把</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">犯</rdg></app>處漸細末。舒掌
<lb n="0171a11" ed="T"/>向下。掌有焰鬘。皆散竪。<note n="0171004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝赤【甲】</note><note n="0171004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦【大】，赤【甲】</note><app n="0171004"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">赤</rdg></app>色以龍為冠鬘
<lb n="0171a12" ed="T"/>瓔珞。手足釧及要<note n="0171005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縚＝物【甲】</note><note n="0171005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縚【大】，物【甲】</note><app n="0171005"><lem wit="【大】">縚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">物</rdg></app>等。頻眉猛視利牙出
<lb n="0171a13" ed="T"/>現。赤色方裙赤色傘蓋。魔王波旬俯伏在地。
<lb n="0171a14" ed="T"/>而四臂通身青色。迴面向上求哀請命。舒右
<lb n="0171a15" ed="T"/>手五指側近額作歸命<note n="0171006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勢＝契【甲】</note><note n="0171006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勢【大】，契【甲】</note><app n="0171006"><lem wit="【大】">勢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">契</rdg></app>。左手<note n="0171007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拈＝拓【甲】</note><note n="0171007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拈【大】，拓【甲】</note><app n="0171007"><lem wit="【大】">拈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拓</rdg></app>地下。二
<lb n="0171a16" ed="T"/>手有一龍。自肘後縛之。髮赤色而散。如有大
<lb n="0171a17" ed="T"/>恐怖之狀。頭近大聖<note n="0171008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左【甲】</note><note n="0171008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，左【甲】</note><app n="0171008"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左</rdg></app>足。本尊左右有一
<lb n="0171a18" ed="T"/>金剛童子。並通身赤色形體光碩。右傍者。右
<lb n="0171a19" ed="T"/>手持桃。<note n="0171009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左＝右【甲】</note><note n="0171009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">左【大】，右【甲】</note><app n="0171009"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">右</rdg></app>執劍向下斫魔王勢。髮向後垂
<lb n="0171a20" ed="T"/>而作赤色。左傍者左挽弓射魔王頭勢。髮髻
<lb n="0171a21" ed="T"/>似赤<note n="0171010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">紗色＝沙【甲】</note><note n="0171010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">紗色【大】，沙【甲】</note><app n="0171010"><lem wit="【大】">紗色</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙</rdg></app>。之<note n="0171011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右字乃至隱十二字甲本作細註</note><note n="0171011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右字却是左左字却是右為隱【大】，(右字却是左左字却是右為隱)【甲】</note><app n="0171011"><lem wit="【大】">右字却是<note n="0171012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左＋（為）【甲】</note><note n="0171012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">左【大】，左為【甲】</note><app n="0171012"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左為</rdg></app>。左字却是右。
<lb n="0171a22" ed="T"/>為<note n="0171013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隱＋（沙音練絹也）【甲】</note><note n="0171013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隱【大】，隱沙音練絹也【甲】</note><app n="0171013"><lem wit="【大】">隱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">隱沙音練絹也</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">右字却是左左字却是右為隱</note></rdg></app>。</p>
